"Pick a Boo" game
 


1. Player chooses several numbers, the amount of numbers chosen show in the Bet button
2. Click on Spin button (Checks the array of numbers played)
3. One Draw number appears & message says if player has won or lost. 
4. When click on Spin button:
   The Pot counter decreases depending how many numbers have been selected by player (ie if picked 5 nbrs, Pot decreases by 5)
5. Player wins = Pot display is updated using Math method increasing Pot by 36.  
   Bet display is reset to 0.
6. Player loses = Bet display is reset to 0.



